Mouzya","basename":"unique0161.uasset.csv","extension":"csv","filename":"unique0161.uasset","path":"data/AnzuAppend/01/DataTable/Scenario/07_Mouzya/unique0161.uasset.csv","data":[["unique0161","unique0161",null,null,null],["13_TEXT","13_TEXT",null,null,null],["「ひぃ……ふぅ……みぃ」","「一……二……三」",null,null,null],["14_TEXT","14_TEXT",null,null,null],["「チッあんだよ！\\n　支払いしょっぼいなァこれで全部かよ」","「啧，什么嘛！\\n　付的钱也太少了吧，这就全拿出来了吗」",null,null,null],["15_TEXT","15_TEXT",null,null,null],["「……ン？　あそこにいるのは」","「……嗯？那边那是」",null,null,null],["16_TEXT","16_TEXT",null,null,null],["「お兄さん、遊んでかなーい？」","「小哥，不来玩玩么——？」",null,null,null],["17_TEXT","17_TEXT",null,null,null],["「なんか見覚えがあるような」","「总觉得有点眼熟啊」",null,null,null],["19_TEXT","19_TEXT",null,null,null],["「へ？　あーーーーー！！\\n　お、お、お、お前はァー！」","「咦？啊——————！！\\n　是、是、是、是你这家伙ー！」",null,null,null],["20_TEXT","20_TEXT",null,null,null],["「……かつて男の子だと勘違いしながら、\\n　共に秘密基地を作った幼馴染の！？」","「……莫非是那个，当初把我误当成男孩子，\\n　还一起搭过秘密基地的青梅竹马！？」",null,null,null],["21_TEXT","21_TEXT",null,null,null],["「は？　全然違ェわ馬鹿。なんそれ」","「哈？才不是呢白痴。你这说的啥啊」",null,null,null],["22_TEXT","22_TEXT",null,null,null],["「……文化圏が違うと、\\n　冗談って一気に通じなくなるよなあ」","「……文化圈不同，\\n　玩笑一下子就讲不通了啊」",null,null,null],["23_TEXT","23_TEXT",null,null,null],["「てめェ！　これィ！\\n　散々な目に遭わせてくれよってー！」","「你这混蛋！就因为你！\\n　可把老子给害惨了你知不知道——！」",null,null,null],["24_TEXT","24_TEXT",null,null,null],["「すまんすまん。\\n　俺も仕事だったからさあ」","「抱歉抱歉。\\n　我也是因为工作嘛」",null,null,null],["25_TEXT","25_TEXT",null,null,null],["「にしてもお前も頑張って\\n　たくましく生活してんだな。よかったよかった」","「话说回来你也挺努力，\\n　过得挺硬朗嘛。太好啦太好啦」",null,null,null],["26_TEXT","26_TEXT",null,null,null],["「こ、こっちは3日に1回しか、\\n　個室のベッドを使えないんだぞ」","「我、我这可是三天才能用一次单人房的床位哎。」",null,null,null],["27_TEXT","27_TEXT",null,null,null],["「……大変そうだな。じゃあ、風呂とかは？」","「……听起来挺不容易的。那，洗澡那些呢？」",null,null,null],["28_TEXT","28_TEXT",null,null,null],["「いや風呂は入らん。うち嫌いだし」","「不不，不洗。反正我也讨厌洗澡。」",null,null,null],["29_TEXT","29_TEXT",null,null,null],["「…………」","「…………」",null,null,null],["30_TEXT","30_TEXT",null,null,null],["「ま、とにかく良かったわ。\\n　そんじゃ、これで」","「嘛，总归是好了。那，就这样吧。」",null,null,null],["33_TEXT","33_TEXT",null,null,null],["「待てこれィ！」","「给我站住！」",null,null,null],["34_TEXT","34_TEXT",null,null,null],["「せめて、買ってけ？　な？」","「至少买点东西再走嘛？行不？」",null,null,null],["35_TEXT","35_TEXT",null,null,null],["「な、なにを」","「买、买什么。」",null,null,null],["36_TEXT","36_TEXT",null,null,null],["「ほんの少しでも責任感感じてるなら、\\n　場所はどこでも良いから、買ってけ？」","「你要是有一丁点内疚的话，随便在哪买点东西再走嘛？」",null,null,null],["37_TEXT","37_TEXT",null,null,null],["「ひ、ひぃ」","「呀、呀啊！」",null,null,null],["38_TEXT","38_TEXT",null,null,null],["「それもダメなら、飯でも奢れー！」","「要连这都不行，就请我搓一顿！」",null,null,null],["39_TEXT","39_TEXT",null,null,null],["「……そのぐらいなら、止む終えなしか……」","「……就这点的话，看来我只能认了……」",null,null,null]],"type":"","context":[["unique0161.uasset.csv/row/104","unique0161.uasset.csv/row/115","unique0161.uasset.csv/row/126","unique0161.uasset.csv/row/137","unique0161.uasset.csv/row/148","unique0161.uasset.csv/row/167","unique0161.uasset.csv/row/178","unique0161.uasset.csv/row/189","unique0161.uasset.csv/row/200","unique0161.uasset.csv/row/211","unique0161.uasset.csv/row/222","unique0161.uasset.csv/row/233","unique0161.uasset.csv/row/244","unique0161.uasset.csv/row/255","unique0161.uasset.csv/row/266","unique0161.uasset.csv/row/277","unique0161.uasset.csv/row/288","unique0161.uasset.csv/row/315","unique0161.uasset.csv/row/326","unique0161.uasset.csv/row/337","unique0161.uasset.csv/row/348","unique0161.uasset.csv/row/359","unique0161.uasset.csv/row/370","unique0161.uasset.csv/row/381"],["unique0161.uasset.csv/row/105"],["unique0161.uasset.csv/row/106"],["unique0161.uasset.csv/row/116"],["unique0161.uasset.csv/row/117"],["unique0161.uasset.csv/row/127"],["unique0161.uasset.csv/row/128"],["unique0161.uasset.csv/row/138"],["unique0161.uasset.csv/row/139"],["unique0161.uasset.csv/row/149"],["unique0161.uasset.csv/row/150"],["unique0161.uasset.csv/row/168"],["unique0161.uasset.csv/row/169"],["unique0161.uasset.csv/row/179"],["unique0161.uasset.csv/row/180"],["unique0161.uasset.csv/row/190"],["unique0161.uasset.csv/row/191"],["unique0161.uasset.csv/row/201"],["unique