669B6D2463B2D1232AD4DBFD3C8D513_2"}],[{"rowInfoText":"TEXT_24_C669B6D2463B2D1232AD4DBFD3C8D513_3"}],[{"rowInfoText":"TEXT_24_C669B6D2463B2D1232AD4DBFD3C8D513_2"}],[{"rowInfoText":"TEXT_24_C669B6D2463B2D1232AD4DBFD3C8D513_3"}],[{"rowInfoText":"TEXT_24_C669B6D2463B2D1232AD4DBFD3C8D513_2"}],[{"rowInfoText":"TEXT_24_C669B6D2463B2D1232AD4DBFD3C8D513_3"}],[{"rowInfoText":"TEXT_24_C669B6D2463B2D1232AD4DBFD3C8D513_2"}],[{"rowInfoText":"TEXT_24_C669B6D2463B2D1232AD4DBFD3C8D513_3"}],[{"rowInfoText":"TEXT_24_C669B6D2463B2D1232AD4DBFD3C8D513_2"}],[{"rowInfoText":"TEXT_24_C669B6D2463B2D1232AD4DBFD3C8D513_3"}],[{"rowInfoText":"TEXT_24_C669B6D2463B2D1232AD4DBFD3C8D513_2"}],[{"rowInfoText":"TEXT_24_C669B6D2463B2D1232AD4DBFD3C8D513_3"}],[{"rowInfoText":"TEXT_24_C669B6D2463B2D1232AD4DBFD3C8D513_2"}],[{"rowInfoText":"TEXT_24_C669B6D2463B2D1232AD4DBFD3C8D513_3"}]],"relPath":"AnzuAppend/01/DataTable/Scenario/04_Oshi/unique0921.uasset.csv","tags":[],"progress":{"translated":95,"length":95,"percent":100},"originalFormat":"Autogenerated TRANS obj","indexIsBuilt":false},"AnzuAppend/01/DataTable/Scenario/04_Oshi/unique0931.uasset.csv":{"dirname":"data/AnzuAppend/01/DataTable/Scenario/04_Oshi","basename":"unique0931.uasset.csv","extension":"csv","filename":"unique0931.uasset","path":"data/AnzuAppend/01/DataTable/Scenario/04_Oshi/unique0931.uasset.csv","data":[["unique0931","unique0931",null,null,null],["13_TEXT","13_TEXT",null,null,null],["「あ、課長。お疲れ様でした」","「啊，课长。您辛苦了。」",null,null,null],["14_TEXT","14_TEXT",null,null,null],["「いやあ。大変な責め苦でしたよ」","「哎呀。真是场要命的拷问啊。」",null,null,null],["15_TEXT","15_TEXT",null,null,null],["「あれ、お椎さんは？」","「咦，椎小姐呢？」",null,null,null],["16_TEXT","16_TEXT",null,null,null],["「疲れて、気絶してしまってね。\\nそれじゃあ掃除の方、よろしく頼むよ」","「太累了，晕过去了。\\n那打扫这边，就拜托你了。」",null,null,null],["17_TEXT","17_TEXT",null,null,null],["「はい。了解しました」","「好的。明白了。」",null,null,null],["20_TEXT","20_TEXT",null,null,null],["「…………………………………………」","「…………………………………………」",null,null,null],["21_TEXT","21_TEXT",null,null,null],["「こ、これは……！」","「这、这是……！」",null,null,null],["22_TEXT","22_TEXT",null,null,null],["「ひえ。何だこれ！\\n一体どんな責め苦が行われていたんだ？！」","「哇。什么鬼！\\n到底用了什么样的拷问才会弄成这样？！」",null,null,null],["23_TEXT","23_TEXT",null,null,null],["「こ、この白い液体は……」","「这、这些白色的液体是……」",null,null,null],["24_TEXT","24_TEXT",null,null,null],["「はっ。触れてしまう度に自らの罪を\\n思い出すと言う霊験あらたかな神水！」","「哈。碰一次就能让你忆起自身罪孽的，\\n灵验无比的圣水！」",null,null,null],["25_TEXT","25_TEXT",null,null,null],["「どうやら凄まじい責苦が\\n行われていたようだな……」","「看来这里刚才进行过\\n非常严酷的拷问啊……」",null,null,null],["26_TEXT","26_TEXT",null,null,null],["27_TEXT","27_TEXT",null,null,null],["「あ…なあ……この紙袋って……何のために……」","「啊……喂……这个纸袋……到底是干啥用的……？」",null,null,null],["28_TEXT","28_TEXT",null,null,null],["「大丈夫ですか、お椎さーん。\\nもう責め苦は終わりましたよ」","「没事吧，小椎？\\n折磨已经结束啦。」",null,null,null],["29_TEXT","29_TEXT",null,null,null],["「…………………………」","「…………………………」",null,null,null],["30_TEXT","30_TEXT",null,null,null],["「返事がない。ただのしかばねのようだ。なんちて」","「没有回应。简直就像一具尸体。开玩笑的啦。」",null,null,null],["31_TEXT","31_TEXT",null,null,null],["「あっはっは、おい。こんなトコでふざけるなってｗｗｗ\\nほら、さっさと起こすぞｗｗｗ」","「啊哈哈，喂。别在这种地方搞笑啦www\\n快，赶紧把她弄醒www」",null,null,null],["34_TEXT","34_TEXT",null,null,null],["「……ぷはっ……かひーっ……かひーっ……かひーっ」","「……噗哈……咳嘶……咳嘶……咳嘶……」",null,null,null],["35_TEXT","35_TEXT",null,null,null],["「大丈夫ですかー？　安心して下さい。もう終わりですよー」","「还好吗？放心吧，已经结束了哦。」",null,null,null],["36_TEXT","36_TEXT",null,null,null],["「紙袋を被せて、\\n呼吸を妨げていたのか……」","「原来是把纸袋套在头上，\\n妨碍她呼吸是吗……」",null,null,null],["37_TEXT","37_TEXT",null,null,null],["「罪の想起だけでなく、窒息までさせられるとは。\\n恐ろしい責め苦だ……」","「不仅让人回想罪行，居然还搞到要让人窒息。\\n这折磨太可怕了……」",null,null,null],["38_TEXT","38_TEXT",null,null,null],["「それにしてはなんか、\\n紙袋に写真が貼っていたような……」","「不过话说回来，我怎么觉得\\n那纸袋上好像贴了张照片……」",null,null,null],["39_TEXT","39_TEXT",null,null,null],["「ひぃー……ひぃーー……ふぅーー……ふぅーー……」","「咿……咿……呼……呼……」",null,null,null],["40_TEXT","40_TEXT",null,null,null],["「息を整えたら、さっさと出てくださいね。\\nこの場所、１０分後には予約入ってるんで」","「气儿喘顺了就赶紧出来吧。\\n这里再过十分钟就有预约了。」",null,null,null],["41_TEXT","41_TEXT",null,null,null],["「げほっ、げほっ、げほっ」","「咳咳！咳！咳！」",null,null,null],["42_TEXT","42_TEXT",null,null,null],["「清掃入りまーす」","「进来打扫啦。」",null,null,null],["43_TEXT","43_TEXT",null,null,null],["「はっ……はぁっ……はあっ……！\\n　死ぬ……か、と、思っ…………」","「哈啊……哈啊……哈啊……！\\n我真以为自己……要死了……」",null,null,null],["44_TEXT","44_TEXT",null,null,null],["「お疲れ様です」","「辛苦了。」",null,null,null],["45_TEXT","45_TEXT",null,null,null],["「あれ課長？　どうかしました、忘れ物ですか」","「咦，课长？您怎么了，忘了东西吗？」",null,null,null],["46_TEXT","46_TEXT",null,null,null],["「ひぃっ」","「咿！」",null,null,null],["49_TEXT","49_TEXT",null,null,null],["「………………」","「………………」",null,null,null],["50_TEXT","50_TEXT",null,null,null],["「ちょっと忘れ物をしてしまいましてね」","「我好像忘了点东西呢。」",null,null,null],["51_TEXT","51_TEXT",null,null,null],["「ひ、ひぃっ。も、もうやめて下さい！\\nお願いです！　もうやめて下さい！」","「咿、咿！求、求求你别再来了！\\n求你了！饶了我吧！」",null,null,null],["52_TEXT","52_TEXT",null,null,null],["「大丈夫ですよ。これするだけだから」","「没事的。只是弄这个而已。」",null,null,null],["58_TEXT","58_TEXT",null,null,null],["「ひっ…………ひぃ……っ、ぃい……ぃ…………」","「咿…………咿……呜、呜……呜…………」",null,null,null],["63_TEXT","63_TEXT",null,null,null],["「…………よし」","「……好了。」",null,null,null],["64_TEXT","64_TEXT",null,null,null],["「それでは、お疲れ様でした。\\nお先に失礼します」","「那，辛苦了。\\n我先走一步了。」",null,null,null],["65_TEXT","65_TEXT",null,null,null],["「はーい、おつかれっしたー」","「好嘞，辛苦啦！」",null,null,null],["66_TEXT","66_TEXT",null,null,null],["「したー」","「辛苦啦！」",null,null,null],["67_TEXT","67_TEXT",null,null,null],["「ひ……はあー……はあー……はあー……はあー……」","「嘶……哈啊……哈啊……哈啊……哈啊……」",null,null,null]],"type":"","context":[["unique0931.uasset.csv/row/104","unique0931.uasset.csv/row/115","unique0931.uasset.csv/row/126","unique0931.uasset.csv/row/137","unique0931.uasset.csv/row/148","unique0931.uasset.csv/row/175","unique0931.uasset.csv/row/186","unique0931.uasset.csv/row/197","unique0931.uasset.csv/row/208","unique0931.uasset.csv/row/219","unique0931.uasset.csv/row/230","unique0931.uasset.csv/row/241","unique0931.uasset.csv/row/252","unique0931.uasset.csv/row/263","unique0931.uasset.csv/row/274","unique0931.uasset.csv/row/285","unique0931.uasset.csv/row/296","unique0931.uasset.csv/row/323","unique0931.uasset.csv/row/334","unique0931.uasset.csv/row/345","unique0931.uass